<!DOCTYPE html><html class="client-nojs" lang="ru" dir="ltr"> <body> <h2><span class="mw-headline" id=".D0.9F.D1.80.D0.B0.D0.B7.D0.B4.D0.BD.D0.B8.D0.BA.D0.B8_.D0.B8_.D0.BF.D0.B0.D0.BC.D1.8F.D1.82.D0.BD.D1.8B.D0.B5_.D0.B4.D0.BD.D0.B8">Праздники и памятные дни</span> </span></h2><h3><span class="mw-headline" id=".D0.9C.D0.B5.D0.B6.D0.B4.D1.83.D0.BD.D0.B0.D1.80.D0.BE.D0.B4.D0.BD.D1.8B.D0.B5">Международные</span> </span></h3><ul><li>Всемирный день борьбы с <a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%91%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%B7%D0%BD%D1%8C_%D0%9F%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%BA%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%81%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%B0" title="Болезнь Паркинсона">болезнью Паркинсона</a>.</li><li><a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9C%D0%B5%D0%B6%D0%B4%D1%83%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B9_%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%8C_%D0%BE%D1%81%D0%B2%D0%BE%D0%B1%D0%BE%D0%B6%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%8F_%D1%83%D0%B7%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2_%D1%84%D0%B0%D1%88%D0%B8%D1%81%D1%82%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B8%D1%85_%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%86%D0%BB%D0%B0%D0%B3%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%B9" title="Международный день освобождения узников фашистских концлагерей">Международный день освобождения узников фашистских концлагерей</a>.</li></ul><h3><span class="mw-headline" id=".D0.9D.D0.B0.D1.86.D0.B8.D0.BE.D0.BD.D0.B0.D0.BB.D1.8C.D0.BD.D1.8B.D0.B5">Национальные</span> </span></h3><ul><li><span style="display: none; speak: none;" class="noprint">Коста-Рика</span><span style="white-space:nowrap;"><span class="flagicon"><a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9A%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0-%D0%A0%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B0" title="Коста-Рика"><img alt="Flag of Costa Rica (state).svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Flag_of_Costa_Rica_%28state%29.svg/22px-Flag_of_Costa_Rica_%28state%29.svg.png" width="22" height="13" class="thumbborder" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Flag_of_Costa_Rica_%28state%29.svg/33px-Flag_of_Costa_Rica_%28state%29.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/